CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625779
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FSeveral Gulf states are now actively
OL,8,Fconsidering military action inside
OL,9,FIran to deter further missile and
OL,10,Fdrone attacks ` a step that would
OL,11,Frepresent a profound escalation and
OL,12,Fone that, until days ago, appeared
OL,13,Fhighly unlikely.
OL,15,FNo decision has been taken, and
OL,16,Fofficials stress that such a move is
OL,17,Ffar from inevitable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625779
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FHowever, ITV News understands that
OL,8,Fsenior officials across a number of
OL,9,FGulf Cooperation Council governments
OL,10,Fare in urgent consultations about what
OL,11,Fcomes next ` not only how to
OL,12,Fstrengthen air defences, but whether
OL,13,Fdeterrence now requires something more
OL,14,Fdirect.
OL,16,F"The Kingdom of Saudi Arabia has
OL,17,Fclearly stated that it does not permit
OL,18,Fthe use of its airspace or territory
OL,19,Fto target Iran and is not a party to
OL,20,Fescalation," a senior Saudi source
OL,21,Ftold ITV News.
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FBut they added: "In light of recent
OL,8,Faggression, the Kingdom reserves the
OL,9,Fright to take all necessary measures
OL,10,Fto safeguard its security, protect its
OL,11,Fterritory, and ensure the safety of
OL,12,Fits citizens and residents."
OL,14,FThe same source stressed that Riyadh
OL,15,Fis pursuing diplomatic channels as
OL,16,F"the only sustainable path" to
OL,17,Fresolving disputes, grounded in
OL,18,Frespect for sovereignty and
OL,19,Finternational law. But the language
OL,20,Fmarks a notable hardening.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@\O]xD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FA senior official from another Gulf
OL,8,Fgovernment said it had been "caught
OL,9,Foff guard" by the scale and scope of
OL,10,FIran's retaliation following the joint
OL,11,FUS and Israeli strikes that began on
OL,12,FSaturday and killed Iran's Supreme
OL,13,FLeader in Tehran.
OL,15,F"It's one thing to hit US bases in the
OL,16,Fregion," the official said ` implying
OL,17,Fthat what followed crossed an unspoken
OL,18,Fthreshold.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@JO]wD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
