CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FFew strategists in Washington or in
OL,8,Fregional capitals expected Iran's
OL,9,Fresponse to move so rapidly beyond
OL,10,FAmerican military targets to civilian
OL,11,Fand energy infrastructure.
OL,13,FA third official described the
OL,14,Fcampaign ` including attempted strikes
OL,15,Fon Dubai and Doha airports ` as an
OL,16,F"existential threat" to states long
OL,17,Fregarded as islands of stability and
OL,18,Finvestment despite their proximity to
OL,19,Fconflict.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
