OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FThe targeting of global critical oil
OL,8,Fand gas facilities over the past 48
OL,9,Fhours, in particular, has forced
OL,10,Fgovernments to coordinate more closely
OL,11,Fand, in some cases, suspend
OL,12,Flongstanding rivalries.
OL,14,FThere is still no certainty that
OL,15,Fleaders in Qatar, Saudi Arabia or the
OL,16,FUnited Arab Emirates would authorise
OL,17,Fstrikes on Iranian territory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FBut officials familiar with the
OL,8,Fdeliberations say the threshold for
OL,9,Fsuch action has shifted markedly `
OL,10,Feven over the course of today.
OL,12,FCapitals that have spent years
OL,13,Fcompeting for influence and investment
OL,14,Fare now weighing decisions that,
OL,15,Fbefore Saturday's strikes, were not
OL,16,Finconceivable ` but were certainly not
OL,17,Fexpected.
OL,19,FThe attacks have included a strike on
OL,20,FSaudi Aramco's Ras Tanura refinery
OL,21,Fearly on Monday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
