OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FA few hours later, Qatar said it
OL,8,Fintercepted two Iranian drones
OL,9,Ftargeting energy facilities, one aimed
OL,10,Fat the major gas hub in Ras Laffan; no
OL,11,Fcasualties were reported.
OL,13,FThis morning, in the UAE, authorities
OL,14,Fin Fujairah confirmed that a fire in
OL,15,Fthe oil industry zone was caused by
OL,16,Fdebris after air defences intercepted
OL,17,Fanother Iranian drone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
