OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDr Hasan Alhasan, Senior Fellow for
OL,13,FMiddle East Policy at the
OL,14,FInternational Institute for Strategic
OL,15,FStudies, said: "The Gulf states are on
OL,16,Fthe front lines of a war they did not
OL,17,Fwant, a war that they sought to avert."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,F"We've seen Iranian UAV attacks
OL,8,Fagainst oil refineries in Saudi Arabia
OL,9,Fand the UAE, and now on gas facilities
OL,10,Fin Qatar.
OL,12,F"And so, essentially, this is meant to
OL,13,Fimpose a cost on the global economy to
OL,14,Finternationalise the conflict in the
OL,15,Fhope that threats to energy security,
OL,16,Fthe threat of a massive price shock to
OL,17,Foil or to gas would essentially force
OL,18,FTrump's hand into ending the conflict
OL,19,Fmore quickly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772625780
OL,3,CGulf states consider military
OL,4,Cintervention in Iran as conflict
OL,5,Cescalates
OL,7,F"What's happening, I think, at the
OL,8,Fmoment is the exact opposite. Iranian
OL,9,Fstrategy is backfiring. It's driving
OL,10,Fand pushing the Gulf state into closer
OL,11,Falignment with the United States."
OL,13,F"There is, I think, a lot of
OL,14,Freluctance on the part of the Gulf
OL,15,Fstates to join a war whose intended
OL,16,Foutcome is unclear. A war that they
OL,17,Fdid not start, that they did not want,
OL,18,Fthat could devolve into an open-ended
OL,19,Fconfrontation, and whose tempo and
OL,20,Fcadence they might not even be able to
OL,21,Fcontrol."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
